# Topo Data, Gestures, And Animations

- Keep SVG/data parsing deterministic in `services/topo`; avoid random IDs or random route attributes in production logic.
- Derive UI-ready route data from real source data or explicit mocks gated to test/dev code paths.
- Keep gesture and zoom behavior predictable; avoid automatic resets after manual interaction.
- Use `react-native-reanimated` and gesture-handler patterns already used in the project.
- Clamp transforms and bounds defensively to prevent erratic pan/zoom behavior.
- When changing interaction semantics, update related decision docs and tests.
